ActBretton Woods and Related Agreements Act
SubjectSpecial Drawing Rights ** International Monetary Fund **
PrecisOrder fixing the sum of money that is equivalent to 1.5 billion Special Drawing Rights as the maximum amount that the Minister of Finance may lend to the INTERNATIONAL MONETARY FUND for the purposes of addressing gaps in international financial institutions' resources and tools to support countries impacted by the COVID-19 crisis.
